## Additional Notes (Non-Binding)

This skill is released for **personal, non-commercial, educational use only**.

It is provided free of cost. The intent is to help individuals improve their own learning through an AI-assisted teaching companion.

While the MIT license permits broad use, the creator asks that you respect the spirit: do not use this as the basis for a paid commercial product or service without separate permission and proper attribution/derivative work handling.

Inspirations and sources are attributed in the README and code comments. This work synthesizes publicly known principles of effective teaching and learning science. No verbatim copyrighted teaching materials from any individual or organization have been copied.
